  "implementation_notes": [
    "HTML element: <hr> with CSS resets is the default. <div role='separator'> is acceptable for non-semantic contexts.",
    "Horizontal: default class only — no modifier. Vertical: add .divider--vertical.",
    "Decorative use: add role='none' aria-hidden='true' to suppress AT announcement.",
    "Vertical divider height requires a parent with a defined height (not height:auto).",
